  "introduction": "Imagine you have two metals: Iron and Gold. If you leave them in the rain for a year, what happens to each? Iron rusts (changes), but Gold stays shiny! Why? Today we unlock the secret code of 'Reactivity' that decides how chemical substances behave.",
